{"tid":1460531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【即時】警方承認派出兩隻鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T03:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:34:35.000Z","uid":261379,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"41471f25ce857ac452aa35d8e55f775a93d2f928","tid":1460531,"uid":261379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">一隻叫你留<br />\n一隻叫你走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你信邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，留同走，睇既其實唔係資訊可信程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（btw，可唔可信<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span></strong>二元分立，係睇<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">程度</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n去到最前線、最戰爭一刻，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">有邊個可以100%信得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n直到811咁多事件，政府已經去到咁撚癲，有邊個夠膽擔保大家既安全，話自己既方法一定無事，有事真係走得到？<br />\n又，咁擔保大家無事係咪唯一指標，用嚟決定去留？<br />\n<em>留得青山在，真係有柴燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">唯一可以信既，就係撫心自問：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你既<strong><em>信念</em></strong>係咩？<br />\n而你，為左呢個信念，<br />\n可以有咩程度既<strong><em>犧牲</em></strong>？<br />\n換言之，你有咩<strong><em>覺悟</em></strong>？</span></span><br />\n<em>唯有<strong>信念</strong>，係可以相信既野；<br />\n抱有同一個信念既人，就係<strong>手足</strong>。<br />\n唯有<strong>覺悟</strong>，係你走落去既泉源：走到無力時再問一次自己係為左啲咩而留/走</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">從今以後，搵鬼既方法得兩步：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">一</span>：<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同</span>信念 <br />\n<strong>&rarr;</strong> <ins><strong>不是同路人</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">二</span>：<span style=\"color: green;\">同</span>信念，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇<strong>同等</strong>覺悟</span></span>既人<br />\n<strong>&rarr;</strong> <ins><strong>佢同你行緊同方向，但未必同一條路</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(佢可能行緊<ins>第二條路</ins>去達成佢既信念，</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但大家都係手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>覺悟程度<span style=\"color: green;\">高</span>既，當然可以<strong>接受</strong>唔同程度既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺悟程度<span style=\"color: green;\">冇咁高</span>既，當然可以<strong>尊重</strong>唔同程度既決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">大家都係手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家都係手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家都係手足</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我有好多好朋友，我又引用朋友既說話作結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n我地每個人都好脆弱。我地係雞蛋，係高牆前面最後都係會粉碎，最多只有剎那的烏托邦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我唔阻止啲人話留守，只要你有粉粹的覺悟。<br />\n我唔阻止啲人話撤退，當你未有粉粹的覺悟。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個艱難既矛盾，希望大家可以一齊走過。或者係呢個時候，最重要嘅唔係fact check唔fact check，而係重新審視自己嘅覺悟。<br />\n<br />\n然後繼續相信同路人。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我，我既信念係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足，咁你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"37177a094b2e4110465bda037fa58ba82bfe68d4","tid":1460531,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed7bc30f9ef1ebe233f7f3cb0943f249e86e056f","tid":1460531,"uid":266635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"影到都唔只兩隻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9871edd64238cf42845062483cafed2d6bdd79e6","tid":1460531,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"[總結] 林鄭：818民陣遊行要人呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9082b15bc300e1f8b5702de4aa6f6967c2c323c","tid":1460531,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e06b66d178dd6a6f1043ce832edddbd4df9522","tid":1460531,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci